<div id="aboutme-section">

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-briefcase about-icon"></span>
I am presently in my last semester of Masters studies. Last summer I interned as an Software Development Engineer at Amazon, Seattle. Previously I have worked as a <strong>software engineer</strong> at Morgan Stanley (full-time), Goldman Sachs (intern) and Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay (intern).
</p>

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-graduation-cap about-icon"></span>
Currently a graduate student in <strong>Computer Science</strong> at the North Carolina State University, with a Bachelor of <strong>Computer Science</strong> from the
Visvesvaraya National Institute of Technology, India. Some of the topics I love reading about includes Machine Learning, AI, Software Development.
</p>

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-code about-icon"></span>
I enjoy writing <strong>useful & reusable software tools</strong> to help others &mdash; check out <a href="/projects">my projects</a>. 
</p>

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-heart about-icon"></span>
I'm addicted to skating, <strong>reading</strong> at any given (and non-given) moment, getting into philosophical debates,
and meeting new people :) 
</p>

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-file-text-o about-icon"></span>
The <strong><a href="/projects">projects</a></strong> page is a nice place to see some of my work, but you can also view my <a href="http://shahrajat.com/resume.pdf" target="_blank">resume</a>. 
</p>

<p class="about-text">
<span class="fa fa-globe about-icon"></span>
Grew up in <i>Khandwa, India</i>, moved to <i>Nagpur, India</i> for undergrad studies, worked in <i>Mumbai</i> after undergrad, flew over continents to <i>North Carolina, USA</i> for grad school.
</p>

</div>

